### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### Get Messages from Chat
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/message/messages/1?page=1&page_size=10&user_id=1

### Add User to Chat
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/message/chat/adduser
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "chat_id": 1,
  "user_id": 3,
  "current_user_id": 1
}

### Get User Chats by User ID (with details)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/message/chats/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": 1
}

# Response format:
# {
#   "chats": [
